All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    ControlRST
    Main class for control module
    ControlThread
    thread started by the 'Control' class for background calculating.
    Guidance
    Main class for 'Hauptseminar AMR' project 'autonomous parking' for students of electrical engineering with specialization 'automation, measurement and control'.
    Guidance.CurrentStatus
    states for the main finite state machine.
    Guidance.CurrentStatusDrive
    states for the sub finite state machine DRIVE
    Guidance.CurrentStatusPark
    states for the sub finite state machine PARK
    Guidance.CurrentStatusParkOut
    states for the sub finite state machine PARK_OUT
    HmiPLT
    HMI server module which collects all relevant robot data and sends them to any connected client.
    HmiPLT.Command
    Enumeration holding all possible message codes.
    HmiReaderThread
    Thread for remote communication via Bluetooth.
    HmiSenderThread
    Thread for remote communication via Bluetooth.
    IControl
    interface for the main module 'Control', providing methods for executing the algorithms to control the robot according to different modes which is set by guidance.
    IControl.ControlMode
    control modes
    IMonitor
    Interface for the module "Monitor"
    IMonitor.monitorMode
    Three modes for monitoring: Online-logging, offline-logging, logging turned off
    INavigation
    interface for the main module 'Navigation', providing methods for estimation of the robot position, its heading angle and information about detected parking slots.
    INavigation.ParkingSlot
    represents one entry in the parking slot data bank.
    INavigation.ParkingSlot.ParkingSlotStatus
    defined states the parking slot can be in
    INxtHmi
    Robot-side human machine interface module.
    INxtHmi.Mode
    Enumeration holding the robot driving modes.
    IPerception
    interface for the main module 'Perception', providing methods for getting all measuring data from the robot sensors
    IPerception.AngleDifferenceMeasurement
    bundles both values relevant for measuring an angle difference by an encoder sensor
    IPerception.EncoderSensor
    supports processing of encoder sensor by recording the angle difference since last call of getEncoderMeasurement and the corresponding time interval.
    IPerception.OdoDifferenceMeasurement
    bundles all values relevant for measuring an shift difference by an Odometry sensor
    IPerception.OdoSensor
    supports processing of the Mouse-odometrysensor by recording the Shift in U-and V-direction since last call of getOdoMeasurement and the corresponding time interval.
    Monitor
    Main class for monitor module
    MonitorThread
    thread started by the 'Monitor' class for background calculating.
    NavigationAT
    Fully functional navigation module / class for the NXT - Robot of the group hsamr1.
    NavigationThread
    thread started by the 'Navigation' class for background calculating.
    PerceptionPMP
    Implementation of IPerception-interface.
    PerceptionThread  
    PID
    PID-controller class
